import React from 'react';
import {
  KeyboardView,
  Title,
  Container,
  Input,
  ButtonSubmit,
  TextButton
} from './styles';
import Header from '../../components/index';

const Register: React.FC = () => {
  return (
    <KeyboardView>
      <Header />
      <Container>
        <Title>Registro</Title>
        <Input
          placeholderTextColor="#000"
          placeholder="nome"
        />
        <Input
          placeholderTextColor="#000"
          placeholder="Sobrenome"
        />
        <Input
          placeholderTextColor="#000"
          placeholder="E-mail"
        />
        <Input
          placeholderTextColor="#000"
          placeholder="Senha"
          secureTextEntry
        />
        <ButtonSubmit>
          <TextButton>
            Registrar
          </TextButton>
        </ButtonSubmit>
      </Container>
    </KeyboardView>
  )
}

export default Register;
